<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Yelpcamp</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/home.css">
  </head>
  <body class="d-flex text-center text-white bg-dark">
    <div class="cover-container d-flex w-100 h-100 p-3 mx-auto flex-column">
      <header class="mb-auto">
        <div>
          <h3 class="float-md-start mb-0">Yelpcamp</h3>
          <nav class="nav nav-masthead justify-content-center float-md-end">
            <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="#">Home</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/campgrounds">Campgrounds</a>
            <% if(!activeUser){ %>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/register">Sign Up</a>
            <% } else{ %>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
            <% } %>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </header>
      <main class="px-3">
        <h1>YelpCamp</h1>
        <p class="lead">Welcome to Yelpcamp! <br>At Yelpcamp, we invite you to embark on an unforgettable outdoor adventure surrounded by nature's grandeur. Nestled amidst serene landscapes and picturesque vistas, our platform serves as your gateway to explore the great outdoors, reconnect with nature, and create lasting memories with loved ones.

            Discover Spectacular Campgrounds
            
            Explore our curated collection of diverse campgrounds, each offering its own unique charm and allure. From secluded forest hideaways to breathtaking mountain vistas and tranquil lakeside retreats, Yelpcamp features an array of camping destinations tailored to satisfy every adventurer's wanderlust.
            
            Plan Your Perfect Getaway
            
            Whether you're a seasoned outdoor enthusiast or a novice camper, Yelpcamp provides all the tools you need to plan your perfect getaway. Browse through detailed campground listings, complete with amenities, activities, and user reviews to help you find the ideal spot for your next outdoor excursion.
            
            Immerse Yourself in Nature's Beauty
            
            Escape the hustle and bustle of city life as you immerse yourself in the tranquility of nature. Wake up to the soothing sounds of chirping birds, breathe in the crisp mountain air, and marvel at the star-studded night skies. With Yelpcamp, the wonders of the natural world are right at your doorstep.
            
            Start Your Adventure Today
            
            Whether you're seeking a weekend retreat, a family camping trip, or an epic wilderness expedition, Yelpcamp is your trusted companion for all your outdoor escapades. Join our community of fellow outdoor enthusiasts, share your camping experiences, and let the spirit of adventure guide you to new horizons.
            
            Experience the Thrill of Camping with Yelpcamp - Where Every Journey Begins</p>
<a href="/campgrounds" class="btn btn-lg btn-secondary font-weight-bold text-dark bg-white">View Campgrounds</a>
      </main>

      <footer class="mt-auto text-white-50">
        <p>&copy; 2024</p>
      </footer>
    </div>

